8:
Yeah. Normally as event organizers,
we specialize in music and
photography, but this time we're
doing something different.
10:
It's meant to be a family-friendly
athletic thing. Basically, fun for kids.
13:
Uh-huh... So why are you telling us
about this?
16:
Inaho's an entertainer, ain't she?
And you're her manager.
23:
Leave everything to me! I have the
perfect idea in mind!
30: I did not think this through...
34:
You wish to bend the people to your
will, yes? Then simply make them
lower their guard.
39:
This is starting to sound a lot more
violent than it should be...
44:
Hmm... What about the yokai
performances you usually do?
50:
Mmmm... It is not a bad idea, but it
also does not seem like it will meet
my client's needs...
55:
What are you, an actual entertainer
now?!
60:
She's been harboring visions of
grandeur ever since meeting that
artist Zigza.
68:
Since this is supposed to be an
athletic event aimed at kids, why not
go for something they can actively
participate in?
78: I see.... If we all play together...
82:
That could be just the thing! You are
a genius, Stella!
87:
Uh, I'm afraid I don't follow. What
exactly is the plan here?
98:
All right, my little troops! Forward
march!
105: Get ready to focus fire on the enemy!
124: Oh no! I am done for!
130:
Excellent work! Keep up the barrage,
everyone!
152:
Didn't think I'd work up such a
sweat...
157:
You were up there for a while. But I
bet we're all gonna feel sore
tomorrow.
167: Hehehe, that is good to hear.
172:
Inaho, why did you want to do this
so badly?
175:
I mean, I know you want to show the
world how awesome yokai can be,
but... I'm impressed with how hard
you worked for this.
179: Why DID I want to do this... Hmm...
187:
Ah, sorry, I didn't mean to put you on
the spot—
191:
I suppose it is because I wish for us
to share in a dream together.
194:
Even if we are all different, we can
enjoy the same things—
198: And in that moment see eye to eye.
202: Huh. Spoken like a true star...
206:
Reminds me that I've been super
into KoiAzu myself lately.
211:
Oho? Well! There is nothing more
inspiring than KoiAzu!
215:
A new character named Tsukuyomi
recently showed up in the story, you
know! His interactions with Lord
Kusanagi have been very intriguing!
219:
Anyway, Stella. I just want you to
know...
223:
I am here for you, and everything
will be fine!
238: Oh, I shall be right there!
242: Mmm! It melts in your mouth!
246:
She completely forgot about
wanting to be popular, didn't she.
249:
Gotta say, regardless of how many
fans she has, she's pretty amazing.
253:
She is. I hope to be more like her one
day.
